-- Slap Integration Tests
-- Each section exercises a feature; assert halts on failure

-- ===== Integer Arithmetic =====
2 3 plus 5 eq assert
10 3 sub 7 eq assert
4 5 mul 20 eq assert
15 4 div 3 eq assert
15 4 mod 3 eq assert
0 1 sub -1 eq assert

-- ===== Booleans =====
true 1 eq assert
false 0 eq assert

-- ===== Float Arithmetic =====
