0 3 (1 plus) repeat 3 eq assert
10 0 (1 plus) repeat 10 eq assert

-- ===== Prelude: isbetween =====
5 1 10 isbetween assert
0 1 10 isbetween not assert
10 1 10 isbetween assert

-- ===== Prelude: lerp =====
0.0 10.0 0.5 lerp 5.0 eq assert
0.0 10.0 0.0 lerp 0.0 eq assert

-- ===== Prelude: fclamp =====
