[10 13 17 22] 2 windows
  (dup 1 get swap 0 get sub) map
[3 4 5] eq assert

-- ===== Complex: rise + select = sort by derived key =====
[30 10 50 20 40] dup rise select [10 20 30 40 50] eq assert

